		<h2><a href="http://cocktails.about.com/b/2014/04/02/2014-about-com-readers-choice-awards-results.htm" zT="1/1jS">2014 About.com Readers' Choice Awards Results</a></h2>
	
	<div class="date">Wednesday April 2, 2014</div>
	<div class="entry"><p>The results are in and we have winners in the <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/tp/2014-Readers-Choice-Awards-Best-Liquors.htm" zT="1/1UH">2014 About.com Readers' Choice Awards</a>.</p>

<div style="margin: 5px 5px 10px; width: 200px; float: right; font-size: 0.8em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://0.tqn.com/d/cocktails/1/0/l/S/-/-/AboutRCA-2014-Winner-Badge.jpg" alt="2014 About.com Readers' Choice Awards" /></div>

<p>Over the last two months readers have been nominating and voting for their favorite distilled spirits in 10 categories and today I get to announce the winning brands. It is an interesting mix and it is apparent that these brands (some of which are relatively unknown) have a strong following and loyal fans. This may be an indication that they're something to try if you haven't already.</p>

<p>Here are the winners in each of the 10 categories. Follow the links to learn a little more about the brand and find a cocktail selected to highlight each.</p>

<ul>
	<li>Best Brandy: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-brandy-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Santa Fe Spirits Apple Brandy</a></li>
	<li>Best Gin: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-gin-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Wheeler's Western Dry Gin</a></li>
	<li>Best Rum: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-rum-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">7 Sirens White Rum</a></li>
	<li>Best Tequila: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-tequila-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Espolon Tequila</a></li>
	<li>Best Vodka: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-vodka-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Pinnacle Vodka</a></li>
	<li>Best Flavored Vodka: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-flavored-vodka-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Pinnacle Cinnabon Vodka</a></li>
	<li>Best Bourbon Whiskey:<a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-bourbon-whiskey-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH"> Bulleit Bourbon Frontier Whiskey</a></li>
	<li>Best Irish Whiskey: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-irish-whiskey-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">The Irishman Single Malt Irish Whiskey</a></li>
	<li>Best Rye Whiskey: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-rye-whiskey-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Redemption Rye Whiskey</a></li>
	<li>Best 'Scotch' Whiskey: <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/Readers-Choice-Awards/l/bl-rca-scotch-whisky-2014winner.htm" zT="1/1UH">Colkegan Single Malt Whiskey</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Remember, this was based solely on reader participation and I am only the facilitator. If 'your brand' didn't make it, there's always next year. The Readers' Choice Awards typically begin in February and you can keep up to date by <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/gi/pages/stay.htm" zT="1/1UH">subscribing to my weekly newsletter</a>.</p>

