		<h2><a href="http://cocktails.about.com/b/2014/04/01/new-cocktail-contest-fruit-cocktails.htm" zT="1/1jS">New Cocktail Contest: Fruit Cocktails</a></h2>
	
	<div class="date">Tuesday April 1, 2014</div>
	<div class="entry"><p>It is April 1st and that means that it is not only April Fool's Day, but also time to announce this <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/cocktail_contest/a/contest_basics.htm" zT="1/1UH">month's cocktail contest</a> and it is the easiest one yet. The theme for April's contest is: Fruit Cocktails.</p>

<div style="margin: 5px 5px 10px; width: 200px; float: right; font-size: 0.8em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://0.tqn.com/d/cocktails/1/0/U/T/-/-/yellow-bird-cocktail.jpg" alt="Yellow Bird Cocktail" /><br />
 <a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/y/r/ylw_brd_cktl.htm" zT="1/1UH">Yellow Bird</a></div>

<p>It's true, all your drink needs this month is a little bit of fruit and I don't care how you get it. Fresh fruits, fruit liquors, purees, nectars, sodas, syrups, and anything else that has a fruit flavor can be used. The only thing I ask is that the fruity flavor be a main component in the drink.</p>

<p>It is a very simple challenge and I'm sure that many of you have a number of cocktails that will work. Choose the best of your creations and share them soon. Deadline on this one is Sunday, April 27th.</p>

<p><a href="http://cocktails.about.com/u/sty/cocktailcontest/Fruit-Cocktail-Contest-April-2014/form.htm" zT="1/1UH">Submit your fruit cocktail here...</a></p>

